editorial.title: Orangeburg
content: Armoni Inn & Suites is located in Orangeburg. Palisades Interstate Park and Rockefeller State Park Preserve reflect the area's natural beauty and area attractions include Rockland Bakery and Lower Hudson Valley Challenger Learning Center. Looking to enjoy an event or a game while in town? See what's happening at Westchester County Center or Yonkers Raceway.

content.text: When visiting Orangeburg, Armoni Inn & Suites is a great choice to consider. You can get a workout in at the fitness center or take a dip in the outdoor pool. Fellow travelers like the helpful staff and comfortable guestrooms.

content.text: • Cooked-to-order breakfast is offered for an extra charge of approximately USD 7.00–16.00 per person
• Rollaway beds are available for USD 30.0 per night

• The seasonal pool is open from June 06 to September 05
  • Children under 16 years old are not allowed in the swimming pool, health club, or fitness facility without adult supervision

This property advises that enhanced cleaning and guest safety measures are currently in place.

Disinfectant is used to clean the property, and commonly-touched surfaces are cleaned with disinfectant between stays.

Personal protective equipment, including masks and gloves, will be available to guests.

Social distancing measures are in place; staff at the property wear personal protective equipment; a shield is in place between staff and guests in main contact areas; periodic temperature checks are conducted on staff; guests are provided with hand sanitizer.

Contactless check-in and contactless check-out are available.

Each guestroom is kept vacant for a minimum of 72 hours between bookings.

This property affirms that it follows the cleaning and disinfection practices of Clean Promise (IHG).
